⠀⠀
As promised here is the FULL TUTORIAL!!!✨
⠀⠀
I’ve been seeing this technique called hydro dipping on Tiktok, Youtube, and here on IG. You can use this technique for many items. I even saw someone dip a iPhone case and it came out really cool✨
⠀⠀⠀
I wanted to make one but of course with a lil Tamara Flare to it. So I added my dazzlers that I always use from Hobby Lobby✨

node.text:
@amazonlive is celebrating Black Owned Businesses this month. It starts today, and I’m so happy to be apart of it!!!✨
⠀⠀⠀
@tamronhall will kick off the event at 3pm Est!!! I go on at 5pm Est/ 4pm CT. I will be featuring some amazing products from black owned business like spices, natural deodorants, coffee etc. Click link in my bio to join✨
⠀⠀⠀
Thank you @amazon for asking me to be apart of this amazing event✨
⠀⠀⠀
#womenownedbusiness #womeninspiringwomen #entrepreneurlife #entrepreneurship #entrepreneurmindset #entrepreneurs #blackownedbusiness #blackowned #blackbusinessmonth #supportsmallbusinesses

node.text:
DIY Dollar Tree Hydro Dip Vase✨
⠀⠀
Neighbor: Can you make me one of those cool marble vases I saw you make on IG✨
Me: You got some 💵. Just playing of course yes, my gift to you✨
⠀⠀⠀
Vases are from Dollar Tree. And I will feature the faux palm plants leaves on my Amazon Live Tonight at 7:30pm CT✨
⠀⠀
If your vase is not the color you want, spray paint it a base color. Let dry. Fill bucket with water. Ad spray paint, mix, and dip. I used white and gold spray paint for the black vase. And for the gold vase, I used black, gold, and white spray paint✨
⠀⠀
I know this video is fast so it’s hard to really learn the technique. I have a extended tutorial on this technique on my IGTV. So head on over there🏃🏽‍♀️ 
⠀⠀

5 min DIY Glam Candle Holder✨
⠀⠀
This glam candle holder takes 5 min or less to make. Pour in your dazzlers from @hobbylobby. Use hot glue gun to adhere your @dollartree vases. Put a candle in the candle holder. Light it and Bam✨
⠀
Cost $5. Quick easy and anyone can do. These would be great for a wedding, bday gathering, brunch, baby shower, etc. on a budget. You can make several and put them on the table as centerpieces✨
⠀⠀
